 ('19', '37', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Oluremi Odutola\",\"slug\":\"oluremi-odutola\",\"postDate\":1464938039,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"28\"],\"4\":\"Manager, Compensation & Benefits\",\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Oluremi is the Manager for Compensation and benefits. A graduate of Ladoke Akintola University of Technology, Oyo&nbsp;State, with&nbsp;a&nbsp;Master of Business Administration (MBA) degree in Human Resources Management, Oluremi started her human resources management career with the defunct Midas Bank plc. in 2001. She later joined Network News 24 (NN24), before joining Brittania-U as compensation and benefits manager and later reassigned as Human Resources Manager.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>In addition to professional experience, she is a member of various local and international human resources bodies.<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"thumbnail\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"22\"]}}', '2016-06-03 07:13:59', '2016-06-03 07:13:59', '70d12a0f-b357-40c1-bb14-8e2be020b8d1'),
