 ('21', '39', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Chibuzor Steve Nwaogu\",\"slug\":\"chibuzor-steve-nwaogu\",\"postDate\":1464938040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"25\"],\"4\":\"Supply Chain Manager: Procurement & Inventory\",\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Chibuzo is Supply Chain Manager for Procurement and Inventory, and he currently heads the Supply Chain & Procurement unit at BUNL.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>He started his career in 1998 as Procurement Officer with Eastern Bulkcem Company Ltd Port Harcourt. He then worked in 2 world class Projects in the Oil and Gas industry: Chevron Nigeria Agbami FPSO Project and Chevron Nigeria Escravos Gas to Liquid Project (EGTL). He joined Chevron Nigeria Agbami FPSO Project in 2007 and later was drafted into the SCM group of Chevron EGTL Project first as a Logistics Specialist and later as Materials De-Inventory coordinator until June 2014. He spent the last 9 years with Chevron Deep Water Agbami FPSO Project and Chevron Escravos Gas to Liquid Project (EGTL).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With about 18 years in Procurement and Logistics Management, he joined the BUNL team as Supply Chain Coordinator: Procurement & Inventory in January 2015.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>He started consulting for Brittania-U on Supply chain management from October 2014 where he built an efficient workflow process to coordinate and manage Procurement; tracking materials movement \\/ usage and maintaining adequate inventory management and control across locations. Very passionate about meeting and exceeding expectations, his dedication and very extensive knowledge of the industry has resulted in the improved performance of BUNL supply chain, creating net value, building a very competitive infrastructure and measuring performance globally.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>A member of American Production and Inventory Control Society \\u2013 APICS, Chartered Institute of Purchasing and Supply \\u2013 CIPS and Associate Member, Nigeria Institute of Management, he wields extensive experience in Supply Chain Management, Procurement, Logistics solutions, Inventory management and Operations.<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"thumbnail\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"19\"]}}', '2016-06-03 07:15:33', '2016-06-03 07:15:33', '6eb4b053-0354-415e-ab2d-fdc1fcd3dfd2'),
