 ('32', '31', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Ahmed Akhter Qazi\",\"slug\":\"ahmed-akhter-qazi\",\"postDate\":1464937680,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"43\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"15\"],\"4\":\"Chief Financial Officer\",\"5\":{\"32\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Currently the Chief Financial Officer at Brittania-U, Ahmed\\u2019s career found root at Schlumberger in Sedco Forex (A Schlumberger Drilling Company) in Oman as Manager Finance & Administration from 1993 \\u2013 1996, after which he proceeded to Indonesia as the Division Controller from 1996 to 1998. He then went on to hold several positions as Controller and Finance Manager for Schlumberger Aberdeen (UK), Libya, Algeria, Saudi Arabia and Pakistan before moving to Iran in 2005. Prior to joining Schlumberger, Qazi had spent eight years in A. F. Ferguson amp;Co Chartered Accountants (PricewaterhouseCoopers- Pakistan) from 1979 to 1986 and then joined Shell Pakistan Limited (formerly Pakistan Burma Shell) as Assistant Chief Accountant from 1986 to 1993.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>He became the Group Finance Director of Nigeria & Gulf of Guinea countries for Schlumberger in June 2011, after spending six years in Iran & Kazakhstan as the Group Finance Controller, also serving as&nbsp;Financial Controller with Fortune 500 and high-tech companies.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>&nbsp;Ahmed holds a Bachelor\\u2019s degree in Commerce from the University of Karachi. He is also a Fellow of the Institute of Chartered Accountants of Pakistan (ICAP) and a Fellow Member of the Institute of Taxation Management of Pakistan. He has also undertaken business administration courses from Institute of Business Administration, Karachi and an advanced financial program from the Wharton School of Business, Pennsylvania. In addition, he was an active member of various social clubs at College level and was an active member of PEG( Pakistan Executive Group-Saudi Arabia).<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"Ahmed Akhter Qazi is the Chief Financial Office of Brittania-U\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"field\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"mainImage\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"16\"]}}', '2016-06-03 09:02:41', '2016-06-03 09:02:41', '08765d01-a6b0-4cd3-8be0-b0d595659dae'),
 ('33', '33', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Nwafor Chukwuemeka Simon\",\"slug\":\"nwafor-chukwuemeka-simon\",\"postDate\":1464937800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"43\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"27\"],\"4\":\"Manager, Exploration & Production\",\"5\":{\"34\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Nwafor is the Manager, Exploration and Production. With over 16 years\\u2019 experience garnered from the Oil & Gas industry in Nigeria and across the globe, Simon is an expert in managing risk complex projects (Hydrocarbon Assets), projects relating to reservoir studies, drilling, on site application supports which includes Seismic interpretation and Reservoir modeling, Coordination of geology & Geophysics seismic interpretation unit, training of the new interpreters, report writing and presentations, Setting up of workstations unit and decision making relating to well proposal, drilling and completions.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>He started his career with a two-year stint at Nigeria Agip oil Company as a&nbsp; geologist , after which he spent three years with Dege Conek Nigeria Limited (Oil & Gas Service Provider) as a Senior Geologist and six years at AnKorPoinTe Integrated Limited, Subsidiary of HBT Consulting, Houston Texas(Oil & Gas Services Provider) as&nbsp; Manager Geology & Geophysicist before joining Brittania-U as&nbsp;Manager,&nbsp;Exploration & Production.<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"thumbnail\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"21\"]}}', '2016-06-03 09:02:51', '2016-06-03 09:02:51', '237813f1-09b1-4af5-8cda-54cf0d7e33f5'),
 ('34', '35', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Julius E. Sea\",\"slug\":\"julius-e-sea\",\"postDate\":1464937860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"43\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"26\"],\"4\":\"Manager, Warri operations\",\"5\":{\"36\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Julius is the manager of Brittania-U\\u2019s Warri Operations. A certified Public Accountant and a certified Information Systems Auditor, He graduated from New Jersey Institute of Technology with a BSc in Management Studies. He further took an MSc. in Accounting from Kean University, New Jersey, after being hired out of college by insurer State Farm as a Senior Insurance Auditor.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>He has worked in the United States for some of the biggest firms in banking, accounting, and insurance \\u2013 State Farm, KPMG, Deloitte, and UBS. He has also provided advisory services to multi-national corporations, including SAS 70, Sarbanes-Oxley, and Integrated Audit covering IT General & Application Controls for clients within the Financial Services & Entertainment Industries.<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"thumbnail\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"20\"]}}', '2016-06-03 09:03:01', '2016-06-03 09:03:01', 'd119908c-7b3f-47d8-9a19-6b7402e50119'),
 ('35', '37', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Oluremi Odutola\",\"slug\":\"oluremi-odutola\",\"postDate\":1464937980,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"43\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"28\"],\"4\":\"Manager, Compensation & Benefits\",\"5\":{\"38\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Oluremi is the Manager for Compensation and benefits. A graduate of Ladoke Akintola University of Technology, Oyo&nbsp;State, with&nbsp;a&nbsp;Master of Business Administration (MBA) degree in Human Resources Management, Oluremi started her human resources management career with the defunct Midas Bank plc. in 2001. She later joined Network News 24 (NN24), before joining Brittania-U as compensation and benefits manager and later reassigned as Human Resources Manager.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>In addition to professional experience, she is a member of various local and international human resources bodies.<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"thumbnail\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"22\"]}}', '2016-06-03 09:03:11', '2016-06-03 09:03:11', '9f0c10d8-fc30-4c47-b71a-fd03f91308d4'),
 ('36', '39', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Chibuzor Steve Nwaogu\",\"slug\":\"chibuzor-steve-nwaogu\",\"postDate\":1464938040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"43\",\"fields\":{\"8\":\"\",\"13\":[\"25\"],\"4\":\"Supply Chain Manager: Procurement & Inventory\",\"5\":{\"40\":{\"type\":\"columns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"column1\":\"<p>Chibuzo is Supply Chain Manager for Procurement and Inventory, and he currently heads the Supply Chain & Procurement unit at BUNL.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>He started his career in 1998 as Procurement Officer with Eastern Bulkcem Company Ltd Port Harcourt. He then worked in 2 world class Projects in the Oil and Gas industry: Chevron Nigeria Agbami FPSO Project and Chevron Nigeria Escravos Gas to Liquid Project (EGTL). He joined Chevron Nigeria Agbami FPSO Project in 2007 and later was drafted into the SCM group of Chevron EGTL Project first as a Logistics Specialist and later as Materials De-Inventory coordinator until June 2014. He spent the last 9 years with Chevron Deep Water Agbami FPSO Project and Chevron Escravos Gas to Liquid Project (EGTL).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With about 18 years in Procurement and Logistics Management, he joined the BUNL team as Supply Chain Coordinator: Procurement & Inventory in January 2015.<\\/p>\",\"column2\":\"<p>He started consulting for Brittania-U on Supply chain management from October 2014 where he built an efficient workflow process to coordinate and manage Procurement; tracking materials movement \\/ usage and maintaining adequate inventory management and control across locations. Very passionate about meeting and exceeding expectations, his dedication and very extensive knowledge of the industry has resulted in the improved performance of BUNL supply chain, creating net value, building a very competitive infrastructure and measuring performance globally.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>A member of American Production and Inventory Control Society \\u2013 APICS, Chartered Institute of Purchasing and Supply \\u2013 CIPS and Associate Member, Nigeria Institute of Management, he wields extensive experience in Supply Chain Management, Procurement, Logistics solutions, Inventory management and Operations.<\\/p>\"}}},\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageIdSourceField\":\"thumbnail\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"},\"12\":[\"19\"]}}', '2016-06-03 09:03:23', '2016-06-03 09:03:23', 'a0f6090c-091e-4989-93c7-379d8ec3c9ff'),
 ('37', '43', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"7\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Board and Executive Team\",\"slug\":\"board-and-executive-team\",\"postDate\":1464944460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<div class=\\\"medium-6 column\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t \\t\\t\\t<p>The Brittania-U board is comprised of industry leaders and key management personnel, well versed in their chosen fields and expertise. Our team is diverse but united by a common goal to build a sustainable company and maintain a strong operational capacity. <\\/p>                  \\r\\n\\t\\t\\t \\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t \\t\\t<div class=\\\"medium-6 column\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t \\t\\t\\t<p>To accomplish this mission, the executive team\\u00a0sets the company\'s goals, policies and objectives. They provide the framework for governance and steer the company\\u2019s business affairs and provide management with guidance in determining the company\\u2019s long-term strategy, and assess company prospects, risks, and controls for risk mitigation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t \\t\\t<\\/div>\",\"3\":{\"seoTitleSource\":\"field\",\"seoTitleSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoTitle\":\"\",\"seoDescriptionSource\":\"custom\",\"seoDescriptionSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoDescription\":\"\",\"seoKeywordsSource\":\"custom\",\"seoKeywordsSourceField\":\"title\",\"seoKeywords\":\"\",\"seoImageIdSource\":\"custom\",\"seoImageId\":\"\",\"twitterCardType\":\"summary\",\"openGraphType\":\"website\",\"robots\":\"\"}}}', '2016-06-03 09:04:02', '2016-06-03 09:04:02', '478c60ce-6858-42ba-966b-c986c8481697'),
