 ('1', '30', 'en_us', '<h5 class=\"text-light c-g\">Mrs. Ifejika has been recognised for her various achievements in the energy sector and in different organisations.</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>In recognition of her sterling leadership/managerial achievements, she has been recognised and won many accolades, some of which are:</p>', '[{\"col1\":\"2012 African Female Energy Leaders of the Year Award in the United - Kingdom by the Center for Economic & Leadership Development\"},{\"col1\":\"The Nigerian Trailblazers Award\"},{\"col1\":\"Montage African Woman of Excellence Award - 2013\"}]', '2016-06-03 06:48:21', '2016-06-03 09:02:29', 'a255a2e6-4149-4380-80d8-dc13f5d37682');



