 ('61', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' vision mission the way we operate and the activities we undertake are expressions of an energetic company operating in utmost sustainability and delivering great results these are embedded in our vision and our mission our vision is to be a profitable and fully integrated nigerian oil gas company of first choice in all aspects our mission is to deliver value in our core business area which covers the entire spectrum of exploration to production refining trading supply distribution our objectives are to contribute to the nation s value creation for the well being of the people better quality of life quality products fair price and job opportunities while ensuring we operate in a safe and clean environment with the aim of ensuring maximum return to our shareholders in this age of fluctuating oil prices we are positioned to adapt to the changing oil market dynamics by responding to local challenges and acting globally while maintaining international standards in our operations '),
